  <brief_title>Docetaxel+Carboplatin vs Epirubicin+Cyclophosphamide Followed by Docetaxel as Adjuvant Treatment in Triple-negative Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Docetaxel Plus Carboplatin Versus Epirubicin Plus Cyclophosphamide Followed by Docetaxel as Adjuvant Treatment in Triple-negative Breast Cancer</official_title>
  <sponsors>
